                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <strong>Summer</strong>
                </td>
                <td>
                    Morning/evening bank &amp; kayak bites
                </td>
                <td>
                    Topwater frogs, spinnerbaits, senkos
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <strong>Fall</strong>
                </td>
